I tried the viral Iced Matcha Ice Cream Float with @naturalicecream Malai Ice Cream which is made with just milk and sugar, and it was so good. I’m not kidding! For more such recipes, follow @naturalicecream #malaimagic #naturals #naturalicecream #tastetheoriginal 

Ingredients:

1 tsp matcha powder
2–3 tbsp hot water
Ice cubes
1–2 scoops Naturals Malai Ice Cream

Instructions:

In a small bowl, whisk the matcha powder with hot water until it’s smooth and slightly frothy.

Add a few ice cubes to a glass.

Scoop 1–2 generous scoops of Naturals Malai Ice Cream over the ice.

Gently pour the matcha over the ice cream. Let it float and slightly melt into a creamy, earthy mix.

Sip, scoop, or stir, enjoy it your way!
